    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility level. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted at Medium model risk given the standardized, single-configuration nature of ASTM F1717 and the conservative acceptance bounds applied. E/uval < 1.96 for all three QoIs; maximum relative error 6.7% against a 10% bound. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
